## MVP Requirements

### Configuration / UX
- [Quick] Prevent modules from spawning on top of each other
- [Quick] Launch KDDW/modern floating window for setup button
- [Quick] Allow saving remembering audio/midi IDs in user config.
- [Quick] Request rename when a node gets its unique name on graph, so parameters/other panels update properly
- [Quick] fix UX oddities with the add component menu (auto highlight when one search item left, have search bar auto activate to allow immediate typing)
- [Medium] Create application launcher (linux .desktop, single entry/exit scripts)
- [Medium] Create better patch load menu (dedicated internal directory)
- [Medium] hide/lock basic parameters (for simplifying patches)

### Component Improvements
- [Quick] Allow `BufferWaveform` samples per X Pixel to be updated via mouse scroll on widget
- [Quick] allow saving an output buffer to audio file
- [Quick] Send Pitchbend Control to `PolyOscillator`
- [Medium] develope glide mechanism for monophonic oscillator (possibly new oscillator component)
- [Medium] Specialized widget for `MidiFilter` (horizontal piano roll, highlight pass-through key ranges).

### New Components
- [Quick] `BufferReverser` -- flip a buffer and play in reverse (buffer in, buffer out)
- [Medium] `StreamRecorder`  -- convert audio stream to buffer (audio in, buffer out)
- [Medium] `Arpeggiator` -- play series of notes relative to pressed notes in a loop (midi in, midi out)
- [Big] `SpectralDrawer` -- Allow a user to build a spectrograph (buffer out)
- [Big] `SpectralFilter` -- Spectrogram of input buffer, with option to filter out frequency bands (buffer in, buffer out) 

### New Patches
- [Quick] basic all pass
- [Quick] basic comb filter
- [Quick] basic reverb
- [Quick] example supersaw
- [Quick] example additive synthesis
  
